Storm of Swords-Chapter 7\">Jon I</a></td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:middle;\">&#160;←</td>\n<td style=\"width:33%; text-align:center; vertical-align:middle; padding-right:0.1em; padding-left:0.1em;\"><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Daenerys I</a></td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:middle;\">→&#160;</td>\n<td style=\"width:33%; text-align:center; vertical-align:middle;\"><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_9\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 9\">Bran I</a></td>\n</tr></tbody></table></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n↓<br /><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_23\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 23\">Daenerys II</a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Synopsis\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Synopsis</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Character_List_appearing.2Fmentioned\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Character List appearing/mentioned</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Places_and_terms_mentioned\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Places and terms mentioned</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References_and_Notes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References and Notes</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Synopsis\">Synopsis</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_8&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Synopsis\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Illyrio_Mopatis\" title=\"Illyrio Mopatis\">Illyrio</a>'s three ships are sailing for <a href=\"/index.php/Pentos\" title=\"Pentos\">Pentos</a>, and <a href=\"/index.php/Daenerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Daenerys Targaryen\">Daenerys</a> is watching her <a href=\"/index.php/Dragon\" title=\"Dragon\">dragons</a> fly over the ocean. <a href=\"/index.php/Barristan_Selmy\" title=\"Barristan Selmy\">Arstan</a> tells her that <a href=\"/index.php/Balerion\" title=\"Balerion\">Balerion</a> was 200 years old when he died during the reign of King <a href=\"/index.php/Jaehaerys_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Jaehaerys I Targaryen\">Jaehaerys the Conciliator</a>. Arstan then speaks of <a href=\"/index.php/Rhaegar_Targaryen\" title=\"Rhaegar Targaryen\">Rhaegar</a>, how bookish he was as a child, always reading. Then one day he read something in a scroll that made him want to be a warrior, and he began training fiercely. Arstan admits that Rhaegar was a great warrior, but he won no battles. \n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tleft\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:252px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Beguiled_Bodyguard_VeronicaV_Jones.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/b/b6/Beguiled_Bodyguard_VeronicaV_Jones.png/250px-Beguiled_Bodyguard_VeronicaV_Jones.png\" width=\"250\" height=\"172\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/b/b6/Beguiled_Bodyguard_VeronicaV_Jones.png/375px-Beguiled_Bodyguard_VeronicaV_Jones.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/b/b6/Beguiled_Bodyguard_VeronicaV_Jones.png/500px-Beguiled_Bodyguard_VeronicaV_Jones.png 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Beguiled_Bodyguard_VeronicaV_Jones.png\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Jorah makes unwanted advances on <a href=\"/index.php/Daenerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Daenerys Targaryen\">Daenerys Targaryen</a>, by Veronica V. Jones © Fantasy Flight Games</div></div></div>\n<p>Later, <a href=\"/index.php/Jorah_Mormont\" title=\"Jorah Mormont\">Jorah</a> tells her that Arstan is more than he seems, and warns her not to trust him. The knight advises her to sail for <a href=\"/index.php/Astapor\" title=\"Astapor\">Astapor</a> and buy <a href=\"/index.php/Unsullied\" title=\"Unsullied\">Unsullied</a>, the best trained fighting force in the world. He tells the tale of the <a href=\"/index.php/Three_Thousand_of_Qohor\" title=\"Three Thousand of Qohor\">Three Thousand of Qohor</a>, where a small army of Unsullied defeated a huge <i><a href=\"/index.php/Khalasar\" title=\"Khalasar\">khalasar</a></i> trying to pillage <a href=\"/index.php/Qohor\" title=\"Qohor\">Qohor</a>. The Unsullied are eunuch slaves trained to obey orders absolutely, and they feel no pain. Daenerys agrees that she will force Captain <a href=\"/index.php/Groleo\" title=\"Groleo\">Groleo</a> and Strong <a href=\"/index.php/Belwas\" title=\"Belwas\">Belwas</a> to change course. Ser Jorah then grabs her by the waist and kisses her. Dany tells him he should not have done so, but Jorah talks of her vision in the <a href=\"/index.php/House_of_the_Undying\" title=\"House of the Undying\">House of the Undying</a>, and how the dragon having three heads may mean that she should take two more husbands.\n</p>\n<h2><span id=\"Character_List_appearing/mentioned\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Character_List_appearing.2Fmentioned\">Character List appearing/mentioned</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_8&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Character List appearing/mentioned\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div style=\"column-count:3; column-width:300px;\"> \n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Illyrio_Mopatis\" title=\"Illyrio Mopatis\">Illyrio Mopatis</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Daenerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Daenerys Targaryen\">Daenerys Targaryen</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Barristan_Selmy\" title=\"Barristan Selmy\">Arstan</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Balerion\" title=\"Balerion\">Balerion</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Jaehaerys_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Jaehaerys I Targaryen\">Jaehaerys I Targaryen</a> Jaehaerys the Conciliator</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Rhaegar_Targaryen\" title=\"Rhaegar Targaryen\">Rhaegar Targaryen</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Jorah_Mormont\" title=\"Jorah Mormont\">Jorah Mormont</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Groleo\" title=\"Groleo\">Groleo</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Belwas\" title=\"Belwas\">Belwas</a></li></ul>\n</div>\t\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Places_and_terms_mentioned\">Places and terms mentioned</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_8&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Places and terms mentioned\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div style=\"column-count:3; column-width:300px;\"> \n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Pentos\" title=\"Pentos\">Pentos</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Dragon\" title=\"Dragon\">Dragon</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Astapor\" title=\"Astapor\">Astapor</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Unsullied\" title=\"Unsullied\">Unsullied</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Three_Thousand_of_Qohor\" title=\"Three Thousand of Qohor\">Three Thousand of Qohor</a></li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/index.php/Khalasar\" title=\"Khalasar\">Khalasar</a></i></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Qohor\" title=\"Qohor\">Qohor</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_of_the_Undying\" title=\"House of the Undying\">House of the Undying</a></li></ul>\n</div>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References_and_Notes\">References and Notes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</spa